ita Kamdar features contemporary furniture, including sofas, chairs, and a coffee table. Large windows with sheer curtains allow natural light to flood in. A sculpture and framed artwork enhance the space\u0026#39;s elegance.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-08-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-08-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-08-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-08.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-08-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-10/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563661\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-810x1214.jpg\" alt=\"This modern living room, designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar, features a textured black console, a curved green and beige sofa, a gold accent door, and minimalist decor. Draped white curtains let in natural light.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1214\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-810x1214.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-800x1199.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-10-810x1214.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u0