pg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-14-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-14-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-14-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-14-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMoving through the passageway and into private spaces opposite the more public realm is no less exciting. A commissioned piece depicting a deconstructed Buddhist wheel artwork transforms typical circulation into a dynamic and engaging visual journey. And each space is imbued with personality reflecting every member of the family.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-15/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563666\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A dimly lit bedroom designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar showcases a dark gray color scheme, featuring a sculpture on a black nightstand, a large bed with textured bedding, a checkered floor, and an arched door in the background.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-15-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-16/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563667\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a four-poster bed, textured bedding, decorative pillows, a side table, and two wall-mounted round baskets. The dark wall beautifully complements the room\u0026#39;s neutral tones.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-16-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-17/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563668\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A stylish bedroom corner by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a dark wood bed and a patterned floor of alternating brown and white rectangles.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-17-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-18/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563669\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-810x1191.jpg\" alt=\"A corner room designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a wooden chair, a chest of drawers, and wall art depicting a landscape. Two sculpted heads are elegantly displayed on a stand atop the chest, complemented by the floor\u0026#39;s patterned design.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1191\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-810x1191.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-800x1176.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-768x1129.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-1045x1536.jpg 1045w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-18-810x1191.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOgle-worthy works present themselves in an eclectic mix of personal expressions at every turn including curated surprises, bespoke artifacts, and whimsical details that elicit joy. And yet the house seamlessly flows from one space to another, maintaining continuity through consistent building materials such as wood flooring and plaster walls. What’s more, all artful interior elements, apart from two or three fixtures, were designed and produced in India. Herein lies the conceptual throughline: the full realization and execution by Indian brands and designers, a commitment shared by Studio Nishita Kamdar and the family to supporting local craftsmanship and creativity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-19/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563670\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-810x1216.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bathroom featuring a green marble sink, gold faucet, and artistic wall mural designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar. The glass-tiled shower area adds a touch of elegance.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1216\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-810x1216.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-800x1201.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-768x1153.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-1023x1536.jpg 1023w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-19-810x1216.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“Is luxury space? Is luxury about expensive belongings? Is luxury costly,” asks the principal of her eponymous studio, Nishita Kamdar. “Or is luxury simply living in a space that allows you to appreciate the finer nuances of life and the little things like art, environment, and moments?”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWe now have our answer.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-20/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563671\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-810x1217.jpg\" alt=\"A room designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a vibrant mural of people and animals, complemented by curved wooden and red paneling. A blue shelf with scattered red and white balls adds a playful touch.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1217\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-810x1217.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-800x1202.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-768x1154.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-1022x1536.jpg 1022w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-20-810x1217.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-21/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563672\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-810x1178.jpg\" alt=\"Modern bedroom by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a blue bed and red-accented shelves displaying minimal decor, offering a view into a bathroom with geometric tiles and wooden cabinetry.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1178\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-810x1178.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-800x1163.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-768x1117.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-1056x1536.jpg 1056w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-21-810x1178.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-22/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563673\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar, the bathroom features a blue ribbed wall, an arched mirror, and a black sink perched on a wooden cabinet. Geometric floor tiles add to the charm, while wall art is elegantly captured in the reflection.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-22-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-23/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563674\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A cozy bedroom designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar features a colorful geometric pattern headboard, floral-patterned pillows, and a side table with a ceramic vase. Light filters through sheer curtains, adding a touch of serene elegance.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-23-810x540.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-24/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563675\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-810x1223.jpg\" alt=\"This bathroom, designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar, features two uniquely shaped mirrors, three circular mirrors, and dual brown stone sinks with sleek black faucets.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1223\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-810x1223.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-800x1208.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-768x1160.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-1017x1536.jpg 1017w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-24-810x1223.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/studio-nishita-kamdar-designs-a-soul-stirring-mumbai-residence/aria-studio-nishita-kamdar-25/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-563676\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"A shower area designed by Studio Nishita Kamdar showcases a mosaic tile pattern in earthy tones, with curving bands of black, green, red, and white. A rainfall showerhead and controls are elegantly visible on the wall.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2024/11/Aria-Studio-Nishita-Kamdar-25-810x1215.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo see more of Kamdar’s work, visit \u003ca href=\"https://www.studionishitakamdar.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003estudionishitakamdar.com\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by \u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ishifishy/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003eIshita Sitwala\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2023/10/Joseph-Sgambati-Headshot-Small-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2023/10/Joseph-Sgambati-Headshot-Small.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\" data-cfsrc=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2023/10/Joseph-Sgambati-Headshot-Small-100x100.jpg\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eWith professional degrees in architecture and journalism, New York-based writer Joseph has a desire to make living beautifully accessible. His work seeks to enrich the lives of others with visual communication and storytelling through design. When not writing, he teaches visual communication, theory, and design.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
